1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,256 --> 00:01:37,816
=Episode 28=
(Intertwined Killers)

3
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:39,950
Gun, eyewitnesses,

4
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:41,710
and their testimonies

5
00:01:41,909 --> 00:01:42,790
were three variables.

6
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,952
Whether the police could find the gun

7
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:46,510
or the eyewitness

8
00:01:47,030 --> 00:01:49,590
and whether their testimonies
were favorable to us

9
00:01:50,584 --> 00:01:52,109
were all variables within variables.

10
00:01:52,629 --> 00:01:55,510
There is only one combination
among these variables

11
00:01:56,989 --> 00:01:59,790
where you found the gun
and the eyewitness,

12
00:02:01,030 --> 00:02:03,749
and the eyewitness admitted
to illegally taking the gun

13
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:07,109
and honestly told you
everything they saw.

14
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,550
Only this combination

15
00:02:10,830 --> 00:02:13,310
could prove we acted in self-defense.

16
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:19,469
But the probability of getting
this combination is 4 out of 27,

17
00:02:20,110 --> 00:02:22,509
which is an infinite loop of 0.148.

18
00:02:23,349 --> 00:02:24,110
Rounding it off,

19
00:02:24,629 --> 00:02:27,789
if I rely on you, my chances
of winning are only ten percent.

20
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:32,349
I am a pessimist.

21
00:02:33,069 --> 00:02:34,749
I don't think I have such luck,

22
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:39,069
so it's better to destroy the evidence.

23
00:02:41,629 --> 00:02:44,150
(That night,
I returned to the crime scene.)

24
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:00,870
(I searched for a long time,)

25
00:03:01,789 --> 00:03:03,430
(and found
that Zhou Na's body was gone.)

26
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:27,110
(I seemed to see
someone behind the tree.)

27
00:03:28,990 --> 00:03:30,110
(I was terrified.)

28
00:03:32,949 --> 00:03:35,390
(I don't know if it was
a hallucination caused by fear,)

29
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:37,150
(so I turned and ran.)

30
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,789
I'm just like you.

31
00:03:43,069 --> 00:03:44,568
I found out three months ago

32
00:03:44,568 --> 00:03:46,648
that the body was hidden
in the school's sculpture.

33
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:51,430
When did you give the diary
to Ren Xiaoming?

34
00:03:52,349 --> 00:03:54,229
I handed it to her
before she went abroad.

35
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,710
You can check.

36
00:03:58,110 --> 00:04:01,270
All these years, Ren Xiaoming and I
haven't contacted at all.

37
00:04:02,189 --> 00:04:03,590
I can confirm

38
00:04:03,749 --> 00:04:05,830
the authenticity and validity
of this diary,

39
00:04:05,949 --> 00:04:07,669
both the writing time and the content.

40
00:04:08,629 --> 00:04:09,629
One last question.

41
00:04:10,509 --> 00:04:11,469
How did Zhou Na die?

42
00:04:11,789 --> 00:04:13,310
I stabbed Zhou Na to death with a pen.

43
00:04:17,229 --> 00:04:17,912
Huang.

44
00:04:20,469 --> 00:04:21,229
Please take a look.

45
00:04:21,469 --> 00:04:23,229
If you're okay with it, sign here.

46
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:29,240
(The testimonies
by Bai Shu and Ren Xiaoming)

47
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,429
(sounds plausible,)

48
00:04:30,789 --> 00:04:32,590
(but it feels like
there's something fake.)

49
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:34,030
(Neither of them)

50
00:04:34,309 --> 00:04:37,590
(mentioned the neck fracture
as the fatal injury.)

51
00:04:41,109 --> 00:04:42,968
The testimonies
by Bai Shu and Ren Xiaoming

52
00:04:42,968 --> 00:04:43,869
are so strange.

53
00:04:44,549 --> 00:04:46,584
They said they stabbed
Zhou Na to death with a pen.

54
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:48,789
But the autopsy report states

55
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,424
the victim died from a neck fracture.

56
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:53,309
(Either they are both hiding the truth,)

57
00:04:53,869 --> 00:04:55,950
(or they both really don't know
about the truth.)

58
00:04:56,630 --> 00:04:59,750
(And who took the gun?)

59
00:05:00,150 --> 00:05:01,590
(There was someone else there.)

60
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:07,750
We found the video
from that year at Rest Cemetery.

61
00:05:40,349 --> 00:05:41,590
Pause and replay.

62
00:05:51,309 --> 00:05:52,909
(Who recorded this video?)

63
00:05:54,109 --> 00:05:55,390
(Seems like he dodged back.)

64
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:59,510
Did you watch the video I gave you?
Was it clear?

65
00:06:01,989 --> 00:06:03,429
How did you survive in the water?

66
00:06:06,229 --> 00:06:08,070
My body was modified by aliens.

67
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:09,549
I have two lungs.

68
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:13,950
Are you kidding me?

69
00:06:14,590 --> 00:06:15,590
Everyone has two lungs.

70
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,590
Modification?

71
00:06:19,710 --> 00:06:20,309
Is that so?

72
00:06:22,869 --> 00:06:23,549
Then I have four.

73
00:06:23,909 --> 00:06:24,750
Cut the nonsense.

74
00:06:25,869 --> 00:06:28,549
Wait, I gave you the video.

75
00:06:29,150 --> 00:06:30,950
Does that count as a good deed?

76
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:35,869
Alright, then keep doing good deeds.

77
00:06:35,989 --> 00:06:37,349
Keep up the good work.

78
00:06:37,549 --> 00:06:38,104
Come on.

79
00:06:38,469 --> 00:06:39,190
Alright.

80
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,989
We found that Bai Shu

81
00:06:46,109 --> 00:06:46,712
(Diving club)
bought two sets

82
00:06:46,872 --> 00:06:48,568
of diving equipment in a diving forum.

83
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:50,669
It makes sense.

84
00:06:51,869 --> 00:06:52,830
Zhang Fang didn't lie.

85
00:06:53,349 --> 00:06:55,229
Including Bai Shu,
that makes four lungs.

86
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,869
Huang Zhiqiang, former name Zhang Fang,

87
00:07:25,309 --> 00:07:27,669
changed name to Huang Zhiqiang
after a car accident in 2008,

88
00:07:27,672 --> 00:07:30,072
and joined the construction team
under Jinghe Construction.

89
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:31,309
This construction team

90
00:07:31,789 --> 00:07:33,070
took on the renovation project

91
00:07:33,429 --> 00:07:35,869
of Qidian Middle School
in the summer of 2010.

92
00:07:36,229 --> 00:07:38,630
This is so clear.

93
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:42,390
I killed a person and hid the body.

94
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,270
All in one go.

95
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,190
You admitted it?

96
00:07:45,669 --> 00:07:47,109
Absolutely, no time to waste.

97
00:07:47,309 --> 00:07:48,030
Alright then.

98
00:07:48,030 --> 00:07:50,109
Come, let's talk about your crime story.

99
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:53,390
Crime story.

100
00:07:54,456 --> 00:07:55,229
(2010, Behind Rest Cemetery, Qidaohezi)

101
00:07:55,229 --> 00:07:57,150
(That day I went to find Bai Shu,)

102
00:07:57,830 --> 00:08:00,030
(but saw a woman holding a gun
threatening Bai Shu.)

103
00:08:00,429 --> 00:08:01,390
(I wanted to rush over.)

104
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,109
- (Ren Xiaoming arrived.)
- Run.

105
00:08:03,549 --> 00:08:04,950
Run, now!

106
00:08:12,869 --> 00:08:15,349
(Zhou Na wasn't dead,
picked up the gun and chased them.)

107
00:08:17,549 --> 00:08:18,789
(I couldn't just sit by,)

108
00:08:18,869 --> 00:08:20,030
(so I went up to help.)

109
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:23,390
(To leave no evidence,
I picked up the pen cap.)

110
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:27,830
(I tackled Zhou Na)

111
00:08:28,024 --> 00:08:29,464
(and choked her with the bag strap.)

112
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:38,110
(She tried to reach for her gun,
so I kept choking her.)

113
00:08:58,949 --> 00:09:00,390
(Until she stopped moving.)

114
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:13,949
(Suddenly, I saw Bai Shu coming back,)

115
00:09:19,709 --> 00:09:21,309
(so I grabbed the gun and ran.)

116
00:09:28,189 --> 00:09:30,309
What were your plans
after strangling Zhou Na?

117
00:09:31,110 --> 00:09:31,750
I decided

118
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:34,630
to go back to move the body at night.

119
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:44,909
Who was it?

120
00:09:51,429 --> 00:09:53,176
I dragged the body
to the construction site

121
00:09:53,709 --> 00:09:55,470
and encased it in cement
inside the statue.

122
00:09:55,909 --> 00:09:57,230
Then how did you get into

123
00:09:57,309 --> 00:09:59,510
the construction team
under Jinghe Construction?

124
00:10:00,110 --> 00:10:01,189
They were recruiting.

125
00:10:02,110 --> 00:10:03,750
But you had a disability at the time.

126
00:10:04,309 --> 00:10:05,549
Given your condition,

127
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:08,309
if no one ever helped you,
why would they hire you?

128
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,350
I'm handsome.

129
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,069
Not admitting it?

130
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:16,344
Jinghe Construction has a long-term
cooperative relationship with Ge Wenjun.

131
00:10:16,549 --> 00:10:17,750
Didn't she help you?

132
00:10:20,589 --> 00:10:22,669
Yes, she did.

133
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:25,390
Then they hired me.

134
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:29,350
So what? Is helping
disabled people against the law?

135
00:10:29,789 --> 00:10:33,510
Then why did you jump into the reservoir
right in front of Ge Wenjun?

136
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:38,270
Well, she helped secure a job for me.

137
00:10:38,949 --> 00:10:39,510
It's a favor.

138
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:41,630
I wanted to die and kill myself.

139
00:10:41,909 --> 00:10:43,829
Before I died,
I had to say goodbye to her.

140
00:10:44,270 --> 00:10:45,150
Doesn't it make sense?

141
00:10:45,589 --> 00:10:46,150
Kill yourself?

142
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:47,309
What's wrong?

143
00:10:51,909 --> 00:10:54,630
Someone was waiting underwater
with an oxygen tank for you.

144
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:59,350
You tried to kill yourself?

145
00:11:22,549 --> 00:11:23,390
What's wrong?

146
00:11:24,669 --> 00:11:25,630
Feeling sick?

147
00:11:29,949 --> 00:11:30,630
Acting?

148
00:11:32,669 --> 00:11:33,870
Do you love acting that much?

149
00:11:34,789 --> 00:11:37,189
Who was that act by the reservoir for?

150
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:39,470
Was it for the police,

151
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:42,069
or for Ge Wenjun?

152
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:50,470
I have a grudge against her.

153
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:51,870
I wanted to get back at her.

154
00:11:51,990 --> 00:11:53,429
She's the one who ruined my leg.

155
00:11:53,789 --> 00:11:55,230
So what? I...

156
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:57,789
I-I just wanted to die
right in front of her

157
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,990
to make her regret it
for the rest of her life, okay?

158
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:01,750
If you hate Ge Wenjun so much,

159
00:12:01,909 --> 00:12:03,909
why didn't you
take a knife and kill Ge Wenjun

160
00:12:03,909 --> 00:12:05,390
like you did to Wang Hao back then?

161
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,829
Wait, what now?

162
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:11,470
Officer, that's murder.
It's against the law!

163
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,030
Killing myself isn't.

164
00:12:13,429 --> 00:12:15,309
Besides, I've already killed one person.

165
00:12:15,309 --> 00:12:16,549
I can't just kill more.

166
00:12:17,709 --> 00:12:20,189
Well, I'm heinous, right?

167
00:12:20,309 --> 00:12:22,429
I-I just wanted to end my life.

168
00:12:22,949 --> 00:12:24,510
What? Is it bothering anyone?

169
00:12:24,990 --> 00:12:26,870
Wait. I've told you everything.

170
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:27,789
Why all the questions?

171
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:28,829
So many questions.

172
00:12:28,909 --> 00:12:29,750
Who took the gun?

173
00:12:30,069 --> 00:12:30,789
Me.

174
00:12:30,789 --> 00:12:31,309
Where is it?

175
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:35,549
Threw it in the reservoir.

176
00:12:36,909 --> 00:12:38,350
No, really. Stop asking me.

177
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:40,150
I confessed everything.
Why all the questions?

178
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:41,470
You should go find the gun.

179
00:12:41,909 --> 00:12:44,510
That reservoir is huge,
with meters of mud.

180
00:12:52,189 --> 00:12:53,150
I reckon

181
00:12:54,829 --> 00:12:57,789
it'll take you two or three years
to find it.

182
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:08,470
All three of their testimonies
are suspicious.

183
00:13:09,829 --> 00:13:11,150
We're still far from the truth.

184
00:13:22,230 --> 00:13:24,589
(Zhang Fang's testimony
sounds plausible.)

185
00:13:25,470 --> 00:13:27,309
(But I feel something's fishy.)

186
00:13:29,470 --> 00:13:31,990
(Faking suicide
at this critical moment.)

187
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:33,870
(And right in front of Ge Wenjun.)

188
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,110
(What was this about?)

189
00:13:57,592 --> 00:13:59,160
(Bag strap, pen)

190
00:13:59,350 --> 00:14:00,150
One victim.

191
00:14:00,709 --> 00:14:03,110
Three suspects who claim
to be the murderer.

192
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:07,030
Ren Xiaoming.

193
00:14:09,549 --> 00:14:10,189
Bai Shu.

194
00:14:10,189 --> 00:14:11,709
(Killer?)

195
00:14:11,709 --> 00:14:12,549
And Zhang Fang.

196
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:14,488
(Claim to be the killer)
Their testimonies

197
00:14:14,488 --> 00:14:16,189
of what happened that day

198
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:18,350
have both similarities and differences.

199
00:14:19,470 --> 00:14:21,789
They all claimed they killed Zhou Na.

200
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:25,630
But there are indeed two theories
about the cause of death.

201
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,429
What we need to do now

202
00:14:27,549 --> 00:14:29,789
is to uncover the truth of the case

203
00:14:29,789 --> 00:14:30,909
from their testimonies.

204
00:14:31,909 --> 00:14:32,589
Yanzi.

205
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,616
You act as Ren Xiaoming.

206
00:14:35,128 --> 00:14:35,750
- Okay.
- Huang Yue.

207
00:14:36,429 --> 00:14:37,309
- You, Bai Shu.
- Okay.

208
00:14:37,309 --> 00:14:38,949
Shun, Zhang Fang.

209
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:47,110
Let's go through

210
00:14:47,549 --> 00:14:49,230
each person's statement

211
00:14:49,470 --> 00:14:50,429
following the timeline

212
00:14:51,110 --> 00:14:52,630
to see if there are any discrepancies.

213
00:14:53,432 --> 00:14:54,392
Start with Ren Xiaoming.

214
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:01,110
On that day...

215
00:15:01,589 --> 00:15:03,150
I was on the streets of Qidaohezi

216
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:05,110
and saw Zhou Na coming out of a store.

217
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:06,909
She had a knife in her hand.

218
00:15:07,470 --> 00:15:09,110
So I followed her to Rest Cemetery.

219
00:15:09,709 --> 00:15:12,549
At the cemetery's back hill,
I saw her stab Bai Shu with the knife.

220
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,350
Zhou Na had no knife.

221
00:15:17,829 --> 00:15:18,870
She didn't attack me.

222
00:15:19,709 --> 00:15:22,072
She said she killed Wang Hao.
I told her to turn herself in.

223
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,160
But she was too scared.

224
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,750
Zhou Na was about to leave.

225
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:28,589
But Ren Xiaoming saw blood
on Zhou Na's clothes.

226
00:15:28,589 --> 00:15:30,040
Zhou Na was afraid we'd report her,

227
00:15:30,350 --> 00:15:31,350
so she shot at us.

228
00:15:31,789 --> 00:15:32,510
Not a gun,

229
00:15:32,789 --> 00:15:33,470
but a knife.

230
00:15:33,909 --> 00:15:35,709
Zhou Na was trying to kill you
with the knife.

231
00:15:35,709 --> 00:15:36,270
You're lying.

232
00:15:36,589 --> 00:15:37,789
I killed Zhou Na.

233
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:38,949
I killed Zhou Na.

234
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:39,870
You're lying.

235
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:40,669
You're lying.

236
00:15:40,909 --> 00:15:41,630
You're lying!

237
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:42,589
I killed her with a pen.

238
00:15:42,589 --> 00:15:43,189
It was me.

239
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:43,870
It was me.

240
00:15:46,949 --> 00:15:48,270
Wang Hao's testimony,

241
00:15:48,709 --> 00:15:50,709
combined with the video
provided by Zhang Fang.

242
00:15:51,230 --> 00:15:52,309
We can basically conclude

243
00:15:52,549 --> 00:15:54,008
(Ren Xiaoming and Bai Shu)
both Ren Xiaoming and Bai Shu

244
00:15:54,008 --> 00:15:55,829
hide something in their testimonies.

245
00:15:57,069 --> 00:15:59,270
The actual situation
on the day should be...

246
00:15:59,429 --> 00:16:01,350
Zhou Na was holding a gun,

247
00:16:01,909 --> 00:16:03,750
posing a threat to both of them.

248
00:16:04,390 --> 00:16:06,949
In desperation,
Ren Xiaoming used the pen

249
00:16:07,829 --> 00:16:08,510
to stab Zhou Na.

250
00:16:09,189 --> 00:16:12,110
Whether Zhou Na died instantly
after collapsing,

251
00:16:12,309 --> 00:16:13,909
whether there was secondary harm

252
00:16:14,110 --> 00:16:16,230
and what the method
of that secondary harm was,

253
00:16:16,510 --> 00:16:18,470
became the biggest controversy
in the statements.

254
00:16:20,510 --> 00:16:21,549
Zhou Na died.

255
00:16:22,350 --> 00:16:23,470
I grabbed Bai Shu and ran.

256
00:16:25,789 --> 00:16:27,709
I don't know what happened after that.

257
00:16:27,990 --> 00:16:29,630
Bai Shu grabbed you and ran.

258
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,069
Zhou Na wasn't dead.

259
00:16:31,309 --> 00:16:32,472
She was chasing after them.

260
00:16:32,709 --> 00:16:35,350
I strangled Zhou Na from behind
with the bag strap.

261
00:16:35,709 --> 00:16:36,390
Impossible!

262
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,309
I went back and checked.

263
00:16:38,549 --> 00:16:41,350
Besides the pen in her neck,
Zhou Na had no other injuries.

264
00:16:41,589 --> 00:16:42,589
Bai Shu is lying.

265
00:16:42,872 --> 00:16:43,864
Ren Xiaoming is lying.

266
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:45,150
You're lying.

267
00:16:45,589 --> 00:16:46,230
(You're lying.)

268
00:16:46,429 --> 00:16:47,309
Ren Xiaoming is lying.

269
00:16:47,669 --> 00:16:49,208
Bai Shu is lying. They're both lying.

270
00:16:49,350 --> 00:16:49,909
You're lying.

271
00:16:49,949 --> 00:16:51,069
- You're lying.
- They're both lying.

272
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,630
I strangled Zhou Na!

273
00:16:54,069 --> 00:16:54,750
I killed her.

274
00:16:54,949 --> 00:16:55,990
I killed Zhou Na.

275
00:16:56,189 --> 00:16:56,789
You're lying.

276
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:57,750
You're lying.

277
00:16:58,030 --> 00:16:58,909
They're both lying!

278
00:16:59,470 --> 00:17:00,030
(Zhou Na.)

279
00:17:00,030 --> 00:17:00,829
- I killed her!
- You're lying.

280
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:01,390
You're lying.

281
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:02,309
I killed Zhou Na.

282
00:17:02,309 --> 00:17:02,909
Not you.

283
00:17:12,030 --> 00:17:13,430
(All of you are lying.)

284
00:17:15,470 --> 00:17:18,470
The autopsy results align best
with Zhang Fang's testimony.

285
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:21,629
Therefore, Bai Shu lied?

286
00:17:22,549 --> 00:17:24,109
Bai Shu had decided to turn herself in.

287
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:26,360
Whether death was caused
by the pen or the bag strap

288
00:17:26,470 --> 00:17:28,190
wouldn't make a difference
in sentencing.

289
00:17:28,190 --> 00:17:29,149
So why would she lie?

290
00:17:29,176 --> 00:17:32,472
(Bai Shu)

291
00:17:34,149 --> 00:17:35,109
I have something to say.

292
00:17:36,069 --> 00:17:36,589
Go ahead.

293
00:17:40,589 --> 00:17:41,270
I think

294
00:17:41,624 --> 00:17:42,430
(Killer?)

295
00:17:42,430 --> 00:17:43,149
Ren Xiaoming

296
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:46,309
and Bai Shu.

297
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:50,990
Both of them are red herrings.

298
00:17:51,430 --> 00:17:54,510
Suppose we only have one suspect now.

299
00:17:55,192 --> 00:17:57,208
(Zhang Fang)

300
00:17:58,750 --> 00:17:59,430
Zhang Fang.

301
00:18:01,190 --> 00:18:04,510
Then let's verify his testimony
against the existing evidence

302
00:18:04,789 --> 00:18:05,710
to see if it holds up.

303
00:18:10,309 --> 00:18:13,589
Zhou Na held with a gun
but was strangled by Zhang Fang.

304
00:18:14,069 --> 00:18:17,109
He was a renovation worker
at Qidian Middle School,

305
00:18:17,176 --> 00:18:18,840
making it easy
to hide the body in cement.

306
00:18:19,069 --> 00:18:21,309
Everything Zhang Fang said does hold up.

307
00:18:21,549 --> 00:18:23,470
So I believe this case
isn't that complicated.

308
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:24,869
Zhang Fang is the killer.

309
00:18:25,789 --> 00:18:26,309
Wrong.

310
00:18:26,629 --> 00:18:27,230
What's wrong?

311
00:18:27,869 --> 00:18:29,470
Zhang Fang likes Bai Shu.

312
00:18:29,549 --> 00:18:30,549
If he did it,

313
00:18:30,549 --> 00:18:32,728
he'd choose to call the police
and confess immediately

314
00:18:32,950 --> 00:18:34,109
to protect Bai Shu.

315
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:36,470
Especially Ren Xiaoming is involved too.

316
00:18:37,069 --> 00:18:39,190
They've been close friends
since childhood.

317
00:18:39,470 --> 00:18:41,190
He wouldn't drop the gun
and implicate them.

318
00:18:41,549 --> 00:18:42,789
It is just guesswork.

319
00:18:43,389 --> 00:18:45,336
If everyone were loyal
and played by the rules,

320
00:18:45,549 --> 00:18:46,549
we'd be out of a job.

321
00:18:47,990 --> 00:18:49,950
People can lie.
Only evidence speaks the truth.

322
00:18:50,990 --> 00:18:52,750
Evidence only shows the surface world.

323
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:55,389
The real world is a psychological maze.

324
00:18:55,549 --> 00:18:57,069
You make it too mysterious.

325
00:18:57,144 --> 00:18:58,910
- Only evidence speaks the truth.
- Alright, stop that.

326
00:18:58,910 --> 00:19:00,312
The more mysterious thing is here.

327
00:19:00,829 --> 00:19:01,710
The test results said

328
00:19:02,109 --> 00:19:04,549
in the nib and ink sac of the pen
submitted for testing,

329
00:19:04,670 --> 00:19:06,040
trace amounts of blood were found.

330
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:06,950
Not from human.

331
00:19:09,869 --> 00:19:10,549
What is it then?

332
00:19:12,629 --> 00:19:14,309
After joint analysis by animal experts,

333
00:19:14,488 --> 00:19:16,312
it's preliminarily identified
as deer blood.

334
00:19:17,149 --> 00:19:18,149
Deer blood?

335
00:19:18,670 --> 00:19:20,069
Deer and leopard?

336
00:19:20,270 --> 00:19:21,549
Is this Zootopia?

337
00:19:23,389 --> 00:19:26,069
Finding animal blood
on the murder weapon isn't unusual.

338
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:27,389
In many cases,

339
00:19:27,990 --> 00:19:30,349
killers use animal blood
to contaminate the weapon

340
00:19:30,349 --> 00:19:31,829
to cover their tracks.

341
00:19:32,309 --> 00:19:33,190
But most importantly,

342
00:19:35,030 --> 00:19:36,589
who put that deer blood there?

343
00:19:36,670 --> 00:19:37,750
When was it put there?

344
00:19:39,430 --> 00:19:42,309
None of those three ever mentioned it.

345
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:43,309
Right.

346
00:19:43,309 --> 00:19:43,950
Right.

347
00:19:43,990 --> 00:19:46,670
Such crucial information,
and not one of them said a word.

348
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:50,990
Are they hiding it,
or do they just not know?

349
00:19:52,349 --> 00:19:53,149
Exactly.

350
00:19:53,589 --> 00:19:57,309
On this matter,
those three are strangely in sync.

351
00:20:19,349 --> 00:20:20,549
Delivery to your team.

352
00:20:20,910 --> 00:20:21,464
Thanks.

353
00:20:23,736 --> 00:20:24,888
I'll give it to Captain Li.

354
00:20:26,869 --> 00:20:28,349
Captain Li, you sent this to us?

355
00:20:29,109 --> 00:20:29,869
What is it?

356
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:31,910
The sender is you.

357
00:20:31,990 --> 00:20:34,750
Addressed to the Qidaohezi Police's
Criminal Investigation Unit.

358
00:20:35,670 --> 00:20:36,950
I don't remember it.

359
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,536
(Same-Day Delivery)

360
00:20:50,230 --> 00:20:51,470
A voice recorder?

361
00:20:53,208 --> 00:20:54,744
(Ren Xiaoming, Bai Shu, Zhang Fang
Claim to be the killer)

362
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:03,869
Back then,
you hid the poison in the pastry

363
00:21:04,990 --> 00:21:08,149
and made me kill someone
with my car, didn't you?

364
00:21:08,629 --> 00:21:11,670
What happened in the past is settled.

365
00:21:12,670 --> 00:21:14,109
Now, other than cooperating with me,

366
00:21:15,430 --> 00:21:16,536
you have no other way out.

367
00:21:17,629 --> 00:21:18,750
As long as I'm here,

368
00:21:19,950 --> 00:21:21,272
you won't be related to the body.

369
00:21:23,109 --> 00:21:25,389
I'll always be your shield.

370
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:26,869
What did you say?

371
00:21:27,789 --> 00:21:29,950
You're doing it
for Bai Shu and Ren Xiaoming too.

372
00:21:31,389 --> 00:21:32,869
They're your friends.

373
00:21:34,349 --> 00:21:36,309
The police don't have any evidence now.

374
00:21:38,109 --> 00:21:40,069
It will likely become an unsolved case.

375
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:43,549
They'll never find evidence
in this lifetime.

376
00:21:44,629 --> 00:21:45,950
We'll all be fine.

377
00:21:46,829 --> 00:21:49,149
I don't know if others will be okay,

378
00:21:51,190 --> 00:21:54,069
but no one will take the fall for you.

379
00:21:57,560 --> 00:21:58,950
Zhang Fang jumped into the water.

380
00:21:58,950 --> 00:22:00,030
I saw it with my own eyes.

381
00:22:00,349 --> 00:22:01,829
That woman was Ge Wenjun.

382
00:22:02,230 --> 00:22:03,230
Then she's suspicious.

383
00:22:03,589 --> 00:22:05,470
Those two were talking there
for a long time.

384
00:22:05,470 --> 00:22:07,149
I was too far away to hear a word.

385
00:22:07,589 --> 00:22:08,670
So this is what they said.

386
00:22:09,829 --> 00:22:11,270
What's with this voice recorder?

387
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:13,710
Who sent us such an important clue?

388
00:22:14,149 --> 00:22:15,829
And at such a critical moment.

389
00:22:16,349 --> 00:22:17,510
Then it must be Ge Wenjun.

390
00:22:17,990 --> 00:22:19,109
How could Ge Wenjun possibly

391
00:22:19,109 --> 00:22:21,990
give us evidence
that's so damaging to herself?

392
00:22:24,069 --> 00:22:24,629
Shun.

393
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:29,430
Submit this recording to the station
and apply to file a case.

394
00:22:29,430 --> 00:22:29,950
Understood.

395
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:31,389
You two, come with me.

396
00:22:31,389 --> 00:22:32,309
Let's go to Ge Wenjun.

397
00:22:32,309 --> 00:22:32,950
- Yes.
- Okay.

398
00:22:59,990 --> 00:23:00,670
Excuse me.

399
00:23:02,549 --> 00:23:03,470
Anyone here?

400
00:23:33,549 --> 00:23:34,309
No one upstairs.

401
00:23:34,629 --> 00:23:35,349
Nobody here.

402
00:23:43,829 --> 00:23:44,549
Careful.

403
00:23:46,349 --> 00:23:46,910
Get back.

404
00:24:04,190 --> 00:24:04,869
Ma'am.

405
00:24:20,270 --> 00:24:22,750
Bai Shu, my daughter.

406
00:24:24,349 --> 00:24:25,670
All these years,

407
00:24:26,710 --> 00:24:28,750
you've run away from me

408
00:24:29,990 --> 00:24:31,309
and this home countless times.

409
00:24:33,270 --> 00:24:36,309
I've stayed here, waiting for you
to come back countless times.

410
00:24:39,190 --> 00:24:40,470
But this time,

411
00:24:43,309 --> 00:24:44,829
I won't wait for you anymore.

412
00:24:49,389 --> 00:24:50,789
You've lost me.

413
00:24:57,910 --> 00:24:59,309
I found Zhang Fang.

414
00:25:03,910 --> 00:25:06,710
He'll continue what he hasn't finished.

415
00:25:08,389 --> 00:25:11,030
I figured it out that night

416
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:13,069
he wasn't dead.

417
00:25:14,950 --> 00:25:18,349
Remember
in your senior year of high school,

418
00:25:20,710 --> 00:25:23,589
I took you to learn diving at the beach?

419
00:25:26,430 --> 00:25:27,470
Back then,

420
00:25:27,990 --> 00:25:30,109
you'd always get too nervous

421
00:25:30,589 --> 00:25:32,670
and strap your dive mask too tight,

422
00:25:33,829 --> 00:25:36,549
leaving bruises on your face,

423
00:25:38,190 --> 00:25:41,389
making your eyes bloodshot.

424
00:25:45,309 --> 00:25:46,629
(That night,)

425
00:25:49,910 --> 00:25:50,990
I saw it.

426
00:25:52,389 --> 00:25:55,190
Your eyes were bloodshot.

427
00:25:56,629 --> 00:25:57,869
You had bruises on your face.

428
00:26:11,149 --> 00:26:12,230
My child,

429
00:26:14,349 --> 00:26:16,470
I've always protected you.

430
00:26:20,069 --> 00:26:20,750
But you

431
00:26:22,190 --> 00:26:23,750
joined forces with outsiders

432
00:26:25,309 --> 00:26:26,869
to put on an act to me,

433
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:30,789
lied to me,

434
00:26:33,069 --> 00:26:34,270
and betrayed me.

435
00:26:57,549 --> 00:27:00,750
My daughter, you've done wrong again.

436
00:27:05,069 --> 00:27:06,950
I've said it countless times.

437
00:27:08,950 --> 00:27:10,230
If you do something wrong,

438
00:27:12,510 --> 00:27:14,549
you have to face punishment.

439
00:27:20,549 --> 00:27:21,309
From now on,

440
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:24,990
whatever happens,

441
00:27:27,990 --> 00:27:31,549
it's all because of the mistakes
you made.

442
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:16,829
Xiao...

443
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,109
What's your name again?

444
00:28:19,869 --> 00:28:20,670
Xiaoyu.

445
00:28:21,230 --> 00:28:23,109
Xiaoyu, what are you looking at here?

446
00:28:23,950 --> 00:28:26,750
When will grandma and mom pick me up?

447
00:28:31,230 --> 00:28:32,990
How about I take you grocery shopping?

448
00:28:36,149 --> 00:28:38,869
We'll go to the supermarket
and you can ride the rocking horse.

449
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:45,230
Li, where's my phone?

450
00:28:46,389 --> 00:28:47,270
Why do you need it?

451
00:28:47,430 --> 00:28:48,389
I'll go shopping.

452
00:28:50,149 --> 00:28:50,950
I'll go.

453
00:28:54,069 --> 00:28:54,950
Where are you going?

454
00:28:56,910 --> 00:28:57,829
Go buy groceries.

455
00:28:58,149 --> 00:28:59,869
I'll go. I can do it.

456
00:29:01,430 --> 00:29:04,230
You go to the police station
every day for Xiaoming,

457
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,470
running around like a spinning top.

458
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,990
Alright.

459
00:29:08,349 --> 00:29:09,309
A spinning top?

460
00:29:09,869 --> 00:29:11,430
I haven't even started.

461
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:14,349
Don't you trust me? I...

462
00:29:15,670 --> 00:29:16,829
Don't you trust me?

463
00:29:16,910 --> 00:29:17,950
Keep an eye on Xiaoyu.

464
00:29:18,510 --> 00:29:20,750
Xiaofei... Xiaofei
hasn't left his room all day.

465
00:29:21,149 --> 00:29:22,950
Knock on his door later.

466
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:26,549
Let's stay positive about everything.

467
00:29:26,829 --> 00:29:28,670
Everything will be fine.

468
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:32,910
I'll be back in ten minutes.

469
00:29:36,030 --> 00:29:37,349
I'll go buy groceries.

470
00:30:33,624 --> 00:30:34,629
(Harmony Brings Prosperity)

471
00:30:34,629 --> 00:30:37,349
Mom.

472
00:30:38,629 --> 00:30:40,950
Mom, why are you sleeping on the sofa?

473
00:30:42,109 --> 00:30:43,510
Mom, I'm hungry.

474
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:46,510
Mom.

475
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:47,789
Mom!

476
00:30:49,230 --> 00:30:51,750
Mom fainted again. Mom!

477
00:30:52,589 --> 00:30:54,750
Uncle Li!

478
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:56,549
My mom fainted again!

479
00:30:57,990 --> 00:30:58,910
Uncle Li!

480
00:31:02,712 --> 00:31:03,384
Hello.

481
00:31:07,670 --> 00:31:08,670
Okay, I understand.

482
00:31:10,710 --> 00:31:11,829
We received a report

483
00:31:12,270 --> 00:31:13,030
Xiaoyu is missing.

484
00:31:13,510 --> 00:31:16,789
Surveillance shows Ge Wenjun
took Xiaoyu from Ren Meiyan's home.

485
00:31:17,589 --> 00:31:19,030
Did you mail the voice recorder?

486
00:31:24,829 --> 00:31:27,789
Will you confess yourself,
or should I recap it for you?

487
00:31:28,589 --> 00:31:30,589
This affects not just you,

488
00:31:30,829 --> 00:31:31,910
but also Zhang Fang.

489
00:31:34,349 --> 00:31:36,910
I know what you did to me.

490
00:31:37,336 --> 00:31:38,936
Meet me at the reservoir in 15 minutes.

491
00:31:39,510 --> 00:31:41,829
Otherwise, our deal is off.

492
00:32:04,670 --> 00:32:07,589
(I didn't want to involve Zhang Fang
in my issues with Ren Xiaoming.)

493
00:32:08,589 --> 00:32:11,470
(Only by faking his death
could he truly disappear.)

494
00:32:12,910 --> 00:32:14,470
(But I can't let Ge Wenjun off.)

495
00:32:14,950 --> 00:32:17,230
(I must get solid evidence.)

496
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:19,928
(I had Zhang Fang
help me one last time.)

497
00:32:20,510 --> 00:32:22,629
(To record Ge Wenjun's confession.)

498
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:29,470
I'll turn myself in
at the police station today.

499
00:32:30,389 --> 00:32:32,190
Just admit what you did.

500
00:32:32,629 --> 00:32:33,829
Take the fall of what you did.

501
00:32:43,349 --> 00:32:45,869
(I mailed the voice recorder
before turning myself in.)

502
00:32:46,149 --> 00:32:47,389
- Hello.
- You requested the same-day delivery?

503
00:32:47,549 --> 00:32:48,056
Yes.

504
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:48,856
Okay.

505
00:32:49,670 --> 00:32:52,030
Deliver it by 10:30 AM
the day after tomorrow.

506
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:53,048
The day after tomorrow?

507
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,910
You can book it on the very day.

508
00:32:54,910 --> 00:32:56,120
No need to book days ahead.

509
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,869
I'm leaving today. Please.

510
00:32:58,349 --> 00:32:59,000
Here.

511
00:32:59,000 --> 00:32:59,589
This much?

512
00:32:59,589 --> 00:33:00,349
Deliver it on time.

513
00:33:00,789 --> 00:33:01,400
Got it.

514
00:33:03,608 --> 00:33:05,208
You anonymously mailed
the voice recorder

515
00:33:05,430 --> 00:33:08,309
to distance yourself
from Zhang Fang's faked death.

516
00:33:08,589 --> 00:33:10,230
You're really underestimating Ge Wenjun.

517
00:33:13,230 --> 00:33:15,910
Ge Wenjun saw through the trap
you and Zhang Fang set up.

518
00:33:16,309 --> 00:33:18,670
She found the goggle marks on your face.

519
00:33:19,710 --> 00:33:20,910
You met Ge Wenjun?

520
00:33:21,789 --> 00:33:23,950
Stop asking questions.
Keep telling your story.

521
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:28,190
Did you and Ren Xiaoming
return to the crime scene that day,

522
00:33:28,910 --> 00:33:30,389
inflicting secondary harm on Zhou Na?

523
00:33:36,990 --> 00:33:39,349
We did go back
to the crime scene that day.

524
00:33:40,184 --> 00:33:44,888
(2010, Behind Rest Cemetery, Qidaohezi)

525
00:33:49,149 --> 00:33:50,629
(Ren Xiaoming came back later.)

526
00:33:51,190 --> 00:33:53,589
(But I didn't want her
to know Zhou Na was dead,)

527
00:33:54,349 --> 00:33:56,869
(so I told her Zhou Na had gone.)

528
00:33:58,190 --> 00:33:59,030
I'm fine.

529
00:34:01,109 --> 00:34:02,149
Has Zhou Na gone?

530
00:34:04,950 --> 00:34:05,549
She's gone.

531
00:34:09,669 --> 00:34:10,910
Let me take you back.

532
00:34:12,790 --> 00:34:13,749
I'll go check.

533
00:34:14,910 --> 00:34:15,669
Don't go.

534
00:34:17,269 --> 00:34:19,390
She's already gone.
What's there to check?

535
00:34:20,149 --> 00:34:20,709
Let's go.

536
00:34:23,589 --> 00:34:25,496
Don't go, Xiaoming.

537
00:34:28,950 --> 00:34:29,709
Ren Xiaoming.

538
00:34:32,589 --> 00:34:34,030
Ren Xiaoming, don't go.

539
00:34:35,629 --> 00:34:36,189
Don't.

540
00:34:39,910 --> 00:34:40,549
Don't look.

541
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:47,032
Let's go.

542
00:34:47,189 --> 00:34:47,790
What happened?

543
00:34:49,229 --> 00:34:49,950
What happened?

544
00:34:50,709 --> 00:34:51,669
Don't look.

545
00:34:58,629 --> 00:34:59,470
She's dead.

546
00:35:03,790 --> 00:35:04,629
What are you doing?

547
00:35:11,430 --> 00:35:14,109
Ms. Zhou gave this pen to both of us.

548
00:35:14,549 --> 00:35:17,549
If it's guilty, we're both guilty.

549
00:35:29,870 --> 00:35:30,629
- I'll turn myself in.
- Where are you going?

550
00:35:30,990 --> 00:35:31,790
- Where are you going?
- I'll turn myself in.

551
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:32,990
You can't go.

552
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:34,629
She shot us first.

553
00:35:35,430 --> 00:35:36,830
I acted in self-defense.

554
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,950
It was self-defense.

555
00:35:38,950 --> 00:35:40,790
The gun? Where's the gun?

556
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:42,629
The gun's gone.

557
00:35:42,990 --> 00:35:43,830
No gun.

558
00:35:45,269 --> 00:35:46,430
You can't turn yourself in.

559
00:35:47,470 --> 00:35:48,589
She didn't have a gun.

560
00:35:48,790 --> 00:35:51,350
We can't prove it was self-defense.

561
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:56,470
You go back first. Leave this to me.

562
00:35:57,470 --> 00:35:59,350
You go back to Qingzhou, or go abroad.

563
00:36:00,470 --> 00:36:02,350
Go anywhere, the farther the better.

564
00:36:03,589 --> 00:36:04,109
Go.

565
00:36:05,790 --> 00:36:06,430
I'm begging you.

566
00:36:07,109 --> 00:36:08,549
What about you?

567
00:36:11,510 --> 00:36:12,910
I wish she didn't return.

568
00:36:15,669 --> 00:36:18,790
If she didn't return,
she wouldn't have seen the body.

569
00:36:21,629 --> 00:36:23,109
What did you do about the body?

570
00:36:24,189 --> 00:36:25,470
I wanted to handle it myself.

571
00:36:26,189 --> 00:36:29,589
I didn't want this
to affect Ren Xiaoming's future.

572
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:35,096
(2010, Rest Cemetery, Qidaohezi)

573
00:37:17,870 --> 00:37:18,669
Have water.

574
00:38:14,470 --> 00:38:16,149
Drugging Ren Xiaoming
with sleeping pills

575
00:38:16,870 --> 00:38:18,030
was to hide the body, right?

576
00:38:21,709 --> 00:38:22,269
Yes.

577
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:24,430
So you could hide the body alone?

578
00:38:28,950 --> 00:38:30,910
As long as she didn't know
where the body was,

579
00:38:32,269 --> 00:38:33,229
even if she reported it,

580
00:38:34,470 --> 00:38:37,669
the police couldn't find the body,
then won't file the case.

581
00:38:41,950 --> 00:38:42,510
Indeed.

582
00:38:45,390 --> 00:38:46,870
You touched the pen,

583
00:38:47,430 --> 00:38:49,229
but there'd still be traces at the scene

584
00:38:49,229 --> 00:38:51,430
proving Ren Xiaoming
stabbed Zhou Na with the pen.

585
00:38:52,269 --> 00:38:53,430
Once you were involved,

586
00:38:54,390 --> 00:38:56,870
she'd insist on facing it
with you to the end.

587
00:39:02,269 --> 00:39:03,549
We have evidence,

588
00:39:04,430 --> 00:39:06,870
proving you returned
to the crime scene afterward.

589
00:39:07,709 --> 00:39:09,189
Did you really not hide the body?

590
00:39:14,269 --> 00:39:16,030
Did Bai Shu hide the body alone?

591
00:39:19,749 --> 00:39:21,109
Bai Shu didn't hide the body.

592
00:39:21,976 --> 00:39:26,296
(2010, Behind Rest Cemetery, Qidaohezi)

593
00:39:35,589 --> 00:39:36,350
Is this the spot?

594
00:39:39,430 --> 00:39:40,269
Probably.

595
00:39:41,189 --> 00:39:41,910
Where's the body?

596
00:39:43,149 --> 00:39:44,149
Where's the body?

597
00:39:44,589 --> 00:39:45,470
The body's gone.

598
00:39:46,069 --> 00:39:46,990
How could it disappear?

599
00:39:51,589 --> 00:39:52,629
Did you hide it?

600
00:39:54,709 --> 00:39:55,390
Not me.

601
00:39:56,430 --> 00:39:57,589
How could it be me?

602
00:39:58,669 --> 00:40:01,189
I'm too weak to drag it alone.

603
00:40:01,629 --> 00:40:02,269
Swear it.

604
00:40:03,390 --> 00:40:05,709
I swear, it wasn't me.

605
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:09,510
I don't know why it disappeared.

606
00:40:13,990 --> 00:40:14,950
That's strange.

607
00:40:18,350 --> 00:40:19,709
Was it just a dream?

608
00:40:21,350 --> 00:40:22,510
Was it a hallucination?

609
00:40:25,709 --> 00:40:26,870
Let's say yes.

610
00:40:27,790 --> 00:40:28,910
This is also a nightmare.

611
00:40:32,229 --> 00:40:34,109
If what happened yesterday was real,

612
00:40:35,030 --> 00:40:36,629
the body will appear eventually.

613
00:40:39,030 --> 00:40:40,269
Once the body appears,

614
00:40:41,149 --> 00:40:43,069
we'll be trapped
in this nightmare again.

615
00:40:43,870 --> 00:40:46,030
Xiaoming, don't think that way.

616
00:40:47,749 --> 00:40:50,269
The gun's gone, and the body's missing.

617
00:40:50,749 --> 00:40:53,069
Maybe someone dragged it away.

618
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:57,030
But regardless, let's assume
that person is helping us.

619
00:40:59,149 --> 00:41:01,830
Or maybe Zhou Na isn't dead?

620
00:41:02,229 --> 00:41:04,430
She survived.
And she walked away on her own.

621
00:41:06,310 --> 00:41:08,510
Let's take it as a chance
given to us by heaven.

622
00:41:11,709 --> 00:41:13,269
Chances come with a price.

623
00:41:15,830 --> 00:41:16,390
And you?

624
00:41:17,589 --> 00:41:18,910
What about your chances?

625
00:41:20,350 --> 00:41:22,030
Haven't you always wanted to go out?

626
00:41:22,629 --> 00:41:23,990
You worked so hard to go out.

627
00:41:24,589 --> 00:41:26,149
You paid such a high price for it.

628
00:41:30,510 --> 00:41:32,790
Xiaoming, listen to me.

629
00:41:33,870 --> 00:41:35,950
Go back to Qingzhou
and focus on your studies.

630
00:41:38,030 --> 00:41:39,830
Xiaoming, promise me

631
00:41:40,888 --> 00:41:41,720
to go out

632
00:41:42,488 --> 00:41:45,510
and see the world for me, okay?

633
00:41:47,030 --> 00:41:49,030
Forget everything that happened here.

634
00:41:50,189 --> 00:41:51,390
Don't ever bring it up again.

635
00:41:53,350 --> 00:41:54,950
(Pretend it never happened.)

636
00:41:55,830 --> 00:41:59,549
(Let this matter disappear completely
from both our lives.)

637
00:42:01,109 --> 00:42:02,990
(Let's never see each other again.)

638
00:42:15,672 --> 00:42:19,320
(Qidaohezi, 2010)

639
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
